'''CEPA''' is a center of [[environmental studies]], situated in [[São Francisco do Sul]] and in [[São Bento, Santa Catarina|São Bento]] in the state of [[Santa Catarina (state)|Santa Catarina]], [[Brazil]]. It is part of the [[University of Joinville]] - [[Joinville|UNIVILLE]] and harbours scientists studying the [[ecology]] of the [[Atlantic Forest|Mata atlântica]], the Brazilian Atlantic [[rain forest]] as well as [[marine biology]] and [[plant systematics]].

